Patience  Ama Douye Diri, Wife of Bayelsa State Governor is the Guest Speaker at the Media Women Forum Webinar scheduled for August  22, at 6pm via zoom. She will be speaking on Gender Based Violence: Beyond  the literature.The webinar seeks to also examine the rising cases of rape and domestic violence as part of measures aimed at finding solutions to the social  vices. The Guest Speaker is the fourth Nigerian Governor’s wife to speak at Media Women Forum, Gender-Based  conversational series. Media Women Forum comprises senior female Editors,Broadcasters, Media Owners and Journalism Lecturers  within and outside  Nigeria.It was founded to champion the cause of women and children.